node.text:
🥇 OLYMPIC CHAMPIONS! 🥇 
•
•
I still can’t believe we actually did it! After 4 Olympics and 20 years of diving! An Olympic Gold medal! And to do it with @mattydiver was all the more special! I wish my family was there to see it, but knowing my Husband and Son got to see us (📺) win Olympic Gold is NEXT LEVEL! 🥇🔥🇯🇵🇬🇧
•
•
Massive thank you to everyone who made this possible! You have all played such a huge role in making this happen! 
•
•
#tokyo #tokyo2020 #olympics #olympicchampion
